with info    cite 'configures LDAP client from information from a directory server
ldapprofile tool allows an LDAP client configuration file to be
generated automatically from information contained within a directory
server, according to the schema defined in draft-joslin-config-schema-04.txt.
An interactive script, ldapclient, is
provided for initial client configuration.'
